# <%= packageScope ? packageScope + '/' + name : name %>

Nx monorepo workspace.

## Structure

```
apps/          # Application projects
libs/          # Shared libraries
  common/      # Shared DTOs, interfaces, constants
```

## Commands

```bash
# Run a specific app
pnpm nx serve <app-name>

# Build all affected projects
pnpm nx affected --target=build

# Test all affected projects
pnpm nx affected --target=test

# Generate a new NestJS app
pnpm nx g @nx/nest:application apps/<app-name>

# Generate a new library
pnpm nx g @nx/js:library libs/<lib-name>

# View dependency graph
pnpm nx graph
```
